      "title": "Process Isolation Example - Model link",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## The purpose of these workflows is to walk you through process isolation. \n\nWe'll use a popular model, z_image_turbo, as our test. We use two different text encoders just to show a drop-in-and-isolated replacement but if you only have one of the two you can certainly use it for both nodes.\n\n## Model links\n\n**text_encoders**\n\n- [qwen_3_4b.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_4b.safetensors)\n- [qwen_3_8b_fp8mixed.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/vae-text-encorder-for-flux-klein-9b/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_8b_fp8mixed.safetensors)\n\n**diffusion_models**\n\n- [z_image_turbo_bf16.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/z_image_turbo_bf16.safetensors)\n\n**vae**\n\n- [ae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors)\n\n\nModel Storage Location\n\n```\n📂 ComfyUI/\n├── 📂 models/\n│   ├── 📂 text_encoders/\n│   │      └── qwen_3_4b.safetensors\n│   │      └── qwen_3_8b_fp8mixed.safetensors\n│   ├── 📂 diffusion_models/\n│   │      └── z_image_turbo_bf16.safetensors\n│   └── 📂 vae/\n│          └── ae.safetensors\n```\n\nAs we go through the workflows, we'll be replacing parts of the top workflow with isolated components so you can see how both the custom_node code is written and how the --use-process-isolation code written to make it all work.\n\nThe two other comment boxes will walk you through each step as you progress through the workflows"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
